snippet.title: Vultures Scavengers of Death - TactiCon 2024 trailer
snippet.description:
Play the demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death/?utm_source=tacticontrailer

Salento Valley, post bio-hazard incident - As a VULTURE operative, your mission is to extract material to aid in finding a cure for the infection. Select your agent and prepare for turn-based tactical survival against infected mutants. Find the key to our salvation.

Vultures Scavengers of Death Socials
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death
Website: https://vulturesgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/vsxD6n8P8J
Twitter: https://x.com/VulturesGame

Trailer maker: Kenny Chia, Player Two PR
Music: Rise of the Crawlers by Bonpo
